description:
Expeditie Robikson - Lambik has had it. His mood is ruined by traffic jams, long waiting lines, bills and exhortations. Jerom and Lambik go searching for an uninhabited island to get back to tranquility.

Taxi Tata - One evening, Lambik arrives in a garage full of oldtimers. There's also an old American cab. Lambik takes place behind the wheel, and dreams of a life as a taxi driver. When he awakes, he is with the taxi on a busy intersection in Chicago, in 1930.
name: Expeditie Robikson; Taxi Tata
Alona in the Mystery of the Missing Gold

volume.name: The Return of Lum * Urusei Yatsura Part Four
Zane Grey's Stories of the West
